利亞牛隻抱怨酪農的手太冰。<br />\n零下兩百七十三度，原子停止活動；西伯利亞人終於說：『老天，外面好冷！』<br />\n連登仔：『最近天氣開始轉涼了！』"},{"pid":"ae5aef54b23e0406ea11ab48e4098b54ab013a6a","tid":1024890,"uid":231054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T08:56:53.000Z","msg":"記得前年冬天得3度重要落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23391c79af02631b64ef786a3441bcc1c038c060","tid":1024890,"uid":162037,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ae5aef54b23e0406ea11ab48e4098b54ab013a6a","tid":1024890,"uid":231054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T08:56:53.000Z","msg":"記得前年冬天得3度重要落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:13:04.000Z","msg":"今日個feel有啲似"},{"pid":"850974f5022e58620ae1a52da725c9dff7bd2058","tid":1024890,"uid":146246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:35:02.000Z","msg":"者背出汗"},{"pid":"7c555cd6cc77aaa0ddd5265460c24bb06d3ce059","tid":1024890,"uid":162037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:08:20.000Z","msg":"今日好撚濕凍"},{"pid":"1355a6f70971d007ed75aa0c319b28ebf72f7baa","tid":1024890,"uid":162037,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0076a4ae057a580133e83b8017ff94e6354fe777","tid":1024890,"uid":96406,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T03:18:35.000Z","msg":"真係唔覺得凍囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日本嘅8度凍好多 吸啖氣係會寒到入心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:09:23.000Z","msg":"我都去過東京喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地8度有太陽仲暖過香港落雨既23度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5d417570ea8bbb2991f227d0af41573dc77ede","tid":1024890,"uid":187600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:32:19.000Z","msg":"長袖衫都未洗攞出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgm